Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come watch, it's time for the appearance{\i0}\N{\i1}of the three leaves! (yay){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! I'll have three bowls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Did you eat, eat, eat, eat up your{\i0}\N{\i1}feminine charm along with your food?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait, wait a minute! I'm bad at P.E....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(I heard something good--{\i0}\N{\i1}I've found her weakness... Sorry){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I really want is to have fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my f-r-i-e-n-d-s!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try talking about silly things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like our love lives and other stuff like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My, you are direct!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're arrogant{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And high-handed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...etc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You have no reservations, do you?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the three leaves running wild?!{\i0}\N{\i1}No one can stop them!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I the one who is at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A servant like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama totally isn’t cut out\Nfor cute clothes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Ready, set!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, I, my, ambiguous me! (Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind's asleep... (zzz...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel refreshed! Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the three of us (fever!){\i0}\N{\i1}we have transcendent wisdom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when we're actually together, it's just noisy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(One more time!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look! Going my way forcefully forward! (Go! Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward! Yeah, going my way up! (Jump! Jump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full speed ahead!{\i0}\N{\i1}Thanks for your hard work{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the story of my (wow!){\i0}\N{\i1}kind of strange and unusual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Best and strongest life in history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave her alone or Satan will burst out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a high school girl's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}School life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru! Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru! Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru! Let's pla--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ring the doorbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's play. We can play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You came here in this\Nsweltering heat just to play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll draw for the old maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You came just to play Old Maid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why don't we go somewhere cooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,"Your Birthmarks Have Faded"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"Shaved Ice"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, did you do\Nthe summer homework yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, most of it.\NYou haven't started, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope. Let me see yours once you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tch. How 'bout you, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,How rude! Who did it? It hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Oh my, how silly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You said that pretty loudly, sleepyhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Although you were kind enough to\Ninvite me out, I could not help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It is so nice and cool here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I have been working a lot recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe's shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The maid's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember you saying that you would\Ntake on more hours during summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The store happens to be closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you feel okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's swelling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,A rich girl shouldn't have a lump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,However, I hesitate to have you\Nwork in the front like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It was an accident, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,And it happened because she's overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,M-M-M-Miss Yoko is hurt?\NAnd on her forehead? On her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:05:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What if something happens?!\NOr if she gets a scar?! How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You should get it checked by a doctor!\NYou could go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You {\i0}should see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful advice, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}knew {\i0}it was too early for\NMiss Yoko to start working!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Too soft. Mitsugu, you've\Nalways coddled Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, although you're\Na part-timer, this is still work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot coddle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So, please go rest in the back room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Taking care of yourself is also part of working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I the one who is at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,A servant like me, making my\Ndreams come true by opening this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, it comes to this, all because I hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's because\NI'm such a capable manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}your {\i0}head okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey-- Yamaji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she said you need to rest, so go rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe, will the shop be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?\NHow will I get through today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It sounds like it won't be all right at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's perfect. Hayama,\Nwhy don't you work in Miss Yoko's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What, me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, you weren't doing anything yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who wasn't doing anything,\Ncoming over just to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on it, now that it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I have an extra outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking! Why aren't I\Nwearing what Miss Yoko wears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you understand Japanese?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Futaba. Have you finished changing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. We have Futaba. We'll get to\Nsee her wear these weird clothes--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba wouldn't fit in my clothes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, er, I'm not saying that Futaba has\Na dynamite figure, but I'm just quite small.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Should that make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you see, I haven't grown since my teens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,More specifically, since junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not helping by saying this,\Nand it's not that specific, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's saying that you won't\Ngrow anymore either, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's stop talking about our sizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, the usual girl isn't here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup! We're here temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.80,Main,,0,0,0,,This place always has young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What a fun atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see. They're all delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,But this roll cake is simple and light,\Nbecause it's made of fluffy sponge cake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,and buttercream that melts in your mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,and it goes surprisingly well with Japanese tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,This moist gâteau chocolat has a refined\Nsweetness that pairs perfectly with coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The chocolate is rich and dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:18.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Strawberry Mousse Cake"\NThe mousse in this cake brings out the tangy sweetness of strawberry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:23.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and interweaves it with fresh cream\Nfor a superb harmony you can't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,They all seem delicious. I'll take all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,They're probably just her own impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:34.64,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to compete with Futaba,\Nbut I don't want her thinking I can't do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Welco--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of cake are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're really dressed as a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayama's sister. You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,And you look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:11.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Teru!\NHere, candy to keep you going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I expected no less from a professional baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's a monster's intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. I want to help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to make cakes and sweets with Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That's, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,This is our new gelée.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Full of fruits and containing collagen\Nand vitamin C, it's great for your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to call it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:55.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you think of a good name for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,--She really can't let big sis make sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,--I know!\N--She really can't let big sis make sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,"Derived from Pigs."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"Derived from Pigs"\N"Derived from Pigs."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Derived from Pigs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:07.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sis! You mean, "Derived from Pig Skin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, collagen is derived from pig skin, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But "Derived from Pig Skin" is so hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'll think of a name myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister! Where are you, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you're working part time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, if it isn't Takezono's--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Young Master Takezono,\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you please keep it down?\NMiss Yoko won't be able to rest properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, little boy. Did you come to see Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure she was okay and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You're very kind, Young Master Takezono.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,How adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Your bottom is cute, too. Your birthmarks\Nhave faded already, haven't they.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,--She does everything as she pleases.\N--Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck! I don't care\Nif you're her former servant or maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let her work here!\NNot at this dumb and creepy shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You would be hurt if someone\Nsaid mean things to you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,He just likes older girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. You get a reward for being a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. This is for Yoko\Nso she'll get better quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,The smell's leaking past the container!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,My eyes sting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your sister licensed for these substances?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Does she handle poisonous substances?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko, I have food for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama! Wanna go have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nishiyama! Nishiyama,\NNishiyama, Nishiyama, Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:19.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all Nishiyamas here!\NAnd how many times did you ring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go to a cake shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,This one! I hear the new gelée is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,There were flyers all over school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't spend money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,A camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I want a camera to take\Ncute pictures of my baby with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you haven't given up on that yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We can be together all day long\Nduring summer break, so I should--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So which looks good to you?\NI want this one--wanna split it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,And two of these gelées.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Two Derived from Pigs, coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba, two Pigs, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:16.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Two Pigs, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:19.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Derived from Pigs looks like it'll be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that gelée isn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe, we sold out of Derived from Pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Derived from Pigs is a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone buys Derived from Pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Derived from Pigs looks delicious, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you recovered so quickly, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Hayama's sister's cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Somehow I've felt...\Nstrangely energetic since I ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,And I didn't sleep a wink last night, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she actually okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, she's got energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Isn't that Hayama and company?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome! I'm sorry, but we\Njust sold out of the new gelée.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, there's no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, are these acquaintances of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, well! So you work here,\NHayama? This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is my heart suddenly pounding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! You're a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It's that "cosplay," thing, huh!\NHey, do you call the customers "Master"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a uniform, so it's not cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What? It's totally cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,--Are you listening, Kondo? This is--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sh-She's oblivious to the atmosphere!\N--Are you listening, Kondo? This is--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But I saw this on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't work here. I'm helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Me too, but only when it's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They're truly lifesavers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, Hayama is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,She's unfailingly good with customers,\Nshe works quickly, and she thinks quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Very few people her age are so skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.47,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. Anybody could do that!\NCustomer service is a common student job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that\Nfrom someone who's never done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, I doubt someone as\Noverly proud as you could manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,T-True, it is bit beyond me...\Nsince I'm not brave enough to wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Nishiyama totally isn't cut out\Nfor cute clothes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.71,Main,,0,0,0,,And you only just started this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure getting so emotional\Nsuits a customer service position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, would you like to try your hand\Nat the job? Experience is good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, my hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Five times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't do things that\Nwill complicate our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,My motives were perfectly pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did we have to go\Nto a place Hayama works?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry home and have tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You can have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,They're part of a special order I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Additive-free pet treats.\NGive them to your kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't this yummy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, that might be\Nthe best patisserie in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'd never have guessed Hayama works there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You want more? Sorry, that's all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We aren't open yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you decided to work for me after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What? N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:40.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I prepared everything yesterday,\Njust in case this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, smiling is the key element\Nof customer service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:18:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Hayama's smile was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to match her smile,\Nbut try to look friendlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can't do it, if Hayama can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, why'd you photograph me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:20.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Yours just seems unfriendly,\Nor perhaps I should say unnatural...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama told me that you have a cat\Nyou dote on, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you imagine playing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not a face for customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Was my expression that weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,One moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.14,Main,,0,0,0,,This is hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine, no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,J-Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it your first day? Isn't it great\Nyou get to wear such cute clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I know the truth, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You pretended not to,\Nbut really you enjoyed putting that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Good job, Nishiyama. Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with the sudden praise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,She finally complimented me,\Neven if I don't really get why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, of course! Anything\NHayama can do is a breeze for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:39.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, I am a capable woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.31,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, they work here... and yet\NI let myself be coaxed into wearing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,A dozen financiers, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She acted nice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this about, Sonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I got curious when you suddenly called\Nand gave me the day off, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:14.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Nishiyama said she could do\Nanything Hayama could do, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,When did you make a new uniform, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I made it for Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It turned out too tight across the chest,\Nbut it's just Nishiyama's size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,J-Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,There are so many customers!\NI have to work fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It's difficult for anyone\Nuntil they get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,--Strawberry mousse, roll cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,--Nishikawa...\N--Strawberry mousse, roll cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--Nishikawa...\N-and gâteau chocolat, coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry for the wait.\NWe'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,How about this one? It's new!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, high school girls are joining hands\Nand making merry at my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but our star\NDerived from Pigs is sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like this roll cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Still, I got kitty treats, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,"Middle Camera"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello. Are you here shopping, Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:01.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I need a camera\Nto take pictures of my baby--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why are you making printouts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,To give you as mementos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:12.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I see! And by that you mean\Nyou'll continue to work for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind, just delete those\Nfrom your phone! Delete them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Shino Sonobe.\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative, the poor girl\Non a bread-crust diet, and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life\Nis so entertaini-- I mean, wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm pitch black inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I can't live in luxury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if there's lots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three of us, we can eat it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clever and smart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living resolutely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a full tummy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I spend my days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes me smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Food!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Money..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't say here"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We each have our own happiness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's enjoy life as much as we want{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's crazy and messy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, it's the rock scissors parade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the three of us gather{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For rock, paper, scissors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll tie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it'll never end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The parade's started, and you have to join{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer to one times three{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to know, then come here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Shino...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...and Selina's next-episode preview!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, you're a capable woman,\Nso I leave this to you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.35,0:23:57.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next time: 'Veggies, Meat, Meat,\NMeat, Meat, Meat, Meat, and Fish.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You made me do it, so what's with that reaction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next time: Veggies, Meat, Meat,\NMeat, Meat, Meat, Meat, and Fish"
